---
title: Smart Hoisin-Glazed Shrimp with Stir-Fried Sesame Veggies
description: In this smart bowl, sticky-sweet shrimp top a nutty sesame stir-fry that's packed with delicious veggies. A garnish of toasted peanuts makes this dish the whole package!
